" A_Dream_As_Large as Canada "
35th Year_Anniversary_Terry_Fox_Run
Sunday , November 29th , Tan_Trao_St , Phu_My_Hung , D . 7 , HCMC
Dear_Can Cham_Members & Friends ,
We are pleased to announce that registration is open for the 35th Year_Anniversary_Terry_Fox_Run ! This year , the Run will be held on Sunday , November 29th , 2015 , on Tan_Trao_St , in Phu_My_Hung , District 7 ( Registration : 7 : 00am , Run starts : 8am sharp ) .
Here in HCMC , the Canadian community has been hosting the annual Terry_Fox_Run since 1997 , with last year ’ s drawing an enthusiastic involvement of 16,500 participants and raising an impressive over VND1 , 300,000,000 . We encourage all companies , schools , communities , families and individuals to once again join us on the 5km Run , Walk , Wheel or Ride .
We also encourage participants to follow past practices regarding donations and we also welcome additional donations through purchases of t - shirts and in - kind contributions .
We would also appreciate your consideration in supporting the non - promotional spirit of the run by not bringing or displaying any banners and / or signs ( corporate or commercial ) including on the route .
Please spread the word and gather your friends and colleagues for this community building event and help build awareness in the fight against cancer .
The_Organizing_Committee would like to inform you that the Run ’ s Insurance_Coverage will only cover those participants wearing a number bib . This condition is set by the insurance company in cooperation of the guidelines set by the Terry_Fox_Foundation . Any_Donation_Value when registering is welcome .
To register , please print and fill out the registration form , available for download in both Vietnamese and English and bring with your donation to one of our Site_Registration addresses below :
CanCham office at R.305 , New_World_Hotel_Saigon , 76 Le_Lai_St , D . 1 , HCMC
West_Coast_International_Clinic – Level 1 , 71-79 Dong_Khoi , Dist 1 , HCMC
Canadian_International_School_System – No . 86 , Road 23 , Tan_Phu_Ward , D . 7 , HCMC
Learning_Strategies - A7-36 Mỹ_Gia 1 , Phú_Mỹ_Hưng , P . Tân_Phú , D . 7 , HCMC
The_American_School - 172 Nguyen_Van_Huong_St , Thao_Dien_Ward , D . 2 , HCMC
For more information and registration , please go to the link below : http : / / terryfox.canchamvietnam.org or contact Ms . Hien at hien . do@canchamvietnam.org / +84.90.344.1850
